Class BaseProduct

java.lang.Object
com.andrei.BusinessLogic.MenuItem
com.andrei.BusinessLogic.BaseProduct
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class BaseProduct extends MenuItem
A base products, extends menu item. The calculate methods are implemented as simple getters. Has fields to store information about the product that match those in the description. Calls the super constructor for the title.
